_memory_usage_rate increased from 32.29% to 51.91%, change ratio: 46.6%\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这是根据异常指标数据和节点信息所做的分析。对于故障期间的系统问题，主要的资源瓶颈是来自于 `aiops-k8s-04` 的内存使用率异常。", "trace_analysis_findings": "I have analyzed the trace data for the period from 2025-06-10T18:10:08Z to 2025-06-10T18:23:08Z. Below are the significant anomalies found:\n\n### Detected Trace Keys\n- **Latency Indicators**: `latency_spike`, `timeout`, `slow_response`\n- **Error Types**: `deadline_exceeded`\n- **Call Relationships**: \n  - `checkoutservice->emailservice`\n  - `frontend->adservice`\n  - `checkoutservice->shippingservice`\n  - `checkoutservice->paymentservice`\n  - `checkoutservice->cartservice`\n  - `recommendationservice->productcatalogservice`\n\n### Hypotheses\n1. **Checkout Service and Email Service**\n   - **Reason**: Latency spike from `checkoutservice->emailservice`\n   - **Evidence**: \n     - Normal average duration: 24511.29 ms\n     - Anomaly average duration: 80810.5 ms\n     - Occurrences: 2 times\n\n2. **Frontend and Ad Service**\n   - **Reason**: Deadline exceeded in `frontend->adservice`\n   - **Evidence**:\n     - Status code: 4\n     - Status message: \"context deadline exceeded\"\n     - Occurrences: 1 time\n\n3. **Checkout Service and Shipping Service**\n   - **Reason**: Latency spike from `checkoutservice->shippingservice`\n   - **Evidence**:\n     - Normal average duration: 9415.74 ms\n     - Anomaly average duration: 36193.75 ms\n     - Occurrences: 2 times\n\n4. **Checkout Service and Payment Service**\n   - **Reason**: Latency spike from `checkoutservice->paymentservice`\n   - **Evidence**:\n     - Normal average duration: 13865.84 ms\n     - Anomaly average duration: 45412.0 ms\n     - Occurrences: 1 time\n \n5. **Recommendation Service and Product Catalog Service**\n   - **Reason**: Latency spike from `recommendationservice->productcatalogservice`\n   - **Evidence**:\n     - Normal average duration: 75.24 ms\n     - Anomaly average duration: 117.76 ms\n     - Occurrences: 2 times\n\n### Analysis\nThe primary root causes seem to be centered around the Checkout Service, which is experiencing latency spikes when communicating with multiple downstream services including Email, Shipping, and Payment services. Additionally, context deadline exceeded errors were reported in the communication between the Frontend and Ad Service. These issues could be influencing each other, indicating a potential cascading failure or network bottleneck affecting multiple services.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\", \"timeout\", \"slow_response\", \n    \"deadline_exceeded\",\n    \"checkoutservice->emailservice\", \n    \"frontend->adservice\", \n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\", \n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\", \n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\", \n    \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice->emailservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal avg duration: 24511.29 ms, Anomaly avg duration: 80810.5 ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend->adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"deadline_exceeded\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Status: context deadline exceeded\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal avg duration: 9415.74 ms, Anomaly avg duration: 36193.75 ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal avg duration: 13865.84 ms, Anomaly avg duration: 45412.0 ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal avg duration: 75.24 ms, Anomaly avg duration: 117.76 ms\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nThis output provides a detailed analysis of the potenti